se symptoms.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031594,0.04371,0.054001,0.065554,0.076719,0.088224,0.099955,0.10956,0.11969,0.12776,0.11232,0.070911],"unified_progress":[0.036997,0.058536,0.071324,0.079793,0.089153,0.09548,0.097987,0.1017,0.1026,0.10335,0.091694,0.071381]},{"section":17,"text":"Breast cysts are another possibility, but they often don't shrink after delivery.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.02199,0.034115,0.047965,0.06158,0.075155,0.090545,0.10605,0.11897,0.13086,0.13793,0.11193,0.062918],"unified_progress":[0.032031,0.052546,0.070012,0.080449,0.090429,0.099017,0.10123,0.10474,0.10411,0.10552,0.091082,0.068829]},{"section":18,"text":"Given all these clues, I'm leaning towards fibroadenoma.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.015076,0.031489,0.043406,0.053561,0.061027,0.068307,0.074466,0.079148,0.087624,0.10482,0.16262,0.21846],"unified_progress":[0.018447,0.03505,0.045386,0.056412,0.061986,0.074177,0.078422,0.089811,0.09851,0.10843,0.14307,0.1903]},{"section":19,"text":"It fits the description of being a mobile, hormone-related lump that decreases after childbirth.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018988,0.023941,0.030498,0.037794,0.046835,0.057262,0.071072,0.083164,0.10265,0.13617,0.18944,0.20218],"unified_progress":[0.027018,0.035478,0.045605,0.054984,0.066428,0.081627,0.086346,0.098856,0.11133,0.12192,0.13424,0.13617]},{"section":20,"text":"Plus, it's common in young women, especially during pregnancy.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034995,0.034279,0.041169,0.049257,0.058203,0.06892,0.081566,0.093348,0.10964,0.13168,0.15525,0.14169],"unified_progress":[0.039013,0.043759,0.052774,0.061033,0.070809,0.081737,0.087973,0.098528,0.10606,0.11319,0.12108,0.12405]},{"section":21,"text":"Yeah, that seems to make sense.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.097604