n":5,"text":"First, I need to think about breast lumps in pregnancy.","dimension":13,"group":2,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.15516,0.3119,0.055449,0.090859,0.063279,0.088189,0.049197,0.044077,0.039979,0.036445,0.033191,0.03228],"unified_progress":[0.16587,0.13317,0.060163,0.107,0.078241,0.11309,0.068531,0.067033,0.061972,0.056759,0.04982,0.038344]},{"section":6,"text":"Pregnancy can cause changes in the breasts, like engorgement or cysts.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.06369,0.11373,0.11805,0.11152,0.1056,0.096828,0.089325,0.078175,0.067983,0.06179,0.051111,0.042199],"unified_progress":[0.066484,0.085009,0.10227,0.10262,0.10103,0.099899,0.093911,0.088889,0.079774,0.074145,0.059353,0.046623]},{"section":7,"text":"But this is a discrete mass.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.055624,0.10132,0.11227,0.11084,0.10124,0.091104,0.085979,0.079837,0.073577,0.073712,0.060299,0.054201],"unified_progress":[0.057287,0.080358,0.089122,0.099446,0.099438,0.095025,0.093873,0.091144,0.085997,0.086042,0.069046,0.05322]},{"section":8,"text":"Let's consider possible causes.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.043584,0.089816,0.11383,0.11615,0.10607,0.091116,0.08508,0.078422,0.073797,0.078308,0.063068,0.060761],"unified_progress":[0.044042,0.076334,0.088496,0.1027,0.099418,0.09389,0.097737,0.090187,0.085463,0.091837,0.072679,0.057212]},{"section":9,"text":"Galactoceles come to mind.","dimension":12,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.043049,0.082148,0.096284,0.10333,0.10379,0.098276,0.094297,0.087683,0.081397,0.079812,0.067513,0.062418],"unified_progress":[0.049547,0.069027,0.085188,0.095901,0.099346,0.10252,0.098989,0.095122,0.089208,0.08599,0.070667,0.058492]},{"section":10,"text":"They are benign, filled with milk, and can occur during lactation.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034951,0.074462,0.088412,0.098673,0.1038,0.1039